original_title: モーニング娘。'14コンサートツアー秋 GIVE ME MORE LOVE ～道重さゆみ卒業記念スペシャル～
overview: Live features "Morning Musume.'14 Concert Tour 2014 Aki Give Me More Love - Michishige Sayumi Sotsugyo Kinen Special -" held at Yokohama Arena on November 26, 2014. The leader of Morning Musume/ '14, Sayumi Michishige graduated from the group on this day. Also includes her graduation ceremony.
title: Morning Musume '14 Fall Concert Tour GIVE ME MORE LOVE ~Michishige Sayumi Graduation Commemoration Special~
